76.TitleEnglish: GIANT PHO CHALLENGE AT FAMOUS ORLANDO RESTAURANT | Mr Feast
76.SummaryEnglish:
This video, Mr Feast goes to Twenty Pho Hour in Orlando, Florida and has a go at their $50 giant pho bowl challenge...

I've never actually tried a food challenge, but I've always thought that I could competitively eat if I wanted to, so I thought I would give it a try. I saw a Beard Meats Food video a couple days ago where he completed this challenge, and I realized it was really close to where I live! 

If you can finish the challenge in an hour, the $50 meal isn't free, but you get some merch (including a t-shirt) 'equal to the cost of the bowl'. 

If you guys would like to see more food speedrun challenges like this let me know, I love eating food and have a massive stomach...

77.SummaryEnglish:
This video, Dream goes to The Pizza Bistro in Fort Worth, Texas and has a go at their huge 24" pizza challenge...

I did the math and this pizza is equivalent to 2.9 pizzas! If you can finish the challenge in an hour, the pizza is free and I get another free pizza in the future!

This video, I teamed up with my rival, Daquavis, in a new #MinecraftManhunt challenge. We have to speedrun and beat Minecraft against two hunters, but we swap who is playing every minute! It was hilarious and super intense.

In this challenge Daquavis and I essentially are one player. We share an inventory, health, position, and basically everything else. The idea is that we are swapping who has control of one player. When we are swapped out, we don't know what is happening at all. We see a black screen and hear nothing.
